import React, { Component } from 'react'; import Isotope from 'isotope-layout'; import './portfolio.css'; import Img from './person.jpg'; import Img2 from'./f.jpg'; import Img3 from'./img1.jpg'; import $ from 'jquery'; import p1 from './p1.png'; import p2 from './p2.png'; const select = (f,cls,nme) => { $(".btnp1").removeClass("selectbtn"); $(".btnp1").addClass("btnp"); $(".btnp2").removeClass("selectbtn"); $(".btnp2").addClass("btnp"); $(".btnp3").removeClass("selectbtn"); $(".btnp3").addClass("btnp"); $(".btnp4").removeClass("selectbtn"); $(".btnp4").addClass("btnp"); $(".btnp5").removeClass("selectbtn"); $(".btnp5").addClass("btnp"); $(cls).removeClass("btnp"); $(cls).addClass("selectbtn"); f(nme); } const Portfolio = () => { const [isotope, setIsotope] = React.useState(null); const [filterKey, setFilterKey] = React.useState("react"); React.useEffect(() => { setIsotope( new Isotope(".filter-container", { itemSelector: ".filter-item", layoutMode: "fitRows" }) ); }, []); React.useEffect( () => { if (isotope) { filterKey === "*" ? isotope.arrange({ filter: `*` }) : isotope.arrange({ filter: `.${filterKey}` }); } }, [isotope, filterKey] ); return (

PORTFOLIO







    Online Flight Booking

    An application to search and book flights with Payment Gateway integration.

    It also provides facilities to view, verify, cancel tickets and receive notifications.

    FindDoc

    Practo look alike web app with facility to search hospitals, doctors in your area.

    Allows to book appointments and get online doctor consultations as well.

    Mern Social Demo

    A web app with Instagram like features which allows to follow, connect,make private groups, search for and invite friends.

    Build using MERN stack and Socket.io.

    ChatApp

    Real Time Chat Application with facilty to view active members, chat personally or in group.

    Built using Node.js and Socket.io.

    Order Tracking Platform

    It is a platform that helps users to track their order/parcel online.

    Book product online and get a unique, random tracking number to keep track of the orders with email/messaging facilites and admin side to manage different orders.

    Image Search Engine

    Web app to get different number of images for the searched word built using Reactjs.

    It is to view and search for different images using the Pixabay API.

    Conway's Game of Life

    The board game concerned with cellular automation built using the presented rules.

    A version of the traditional Conway's game of life built using Reactjs.

    Lyric Finder

    A platform to search for different songs and top trending songs information.

    Now get to know the lyrics of the songs that are bugging you.

    Polling App

    This is a voting quiz to view and vote for different presented questions.

    Admin to manage, update and add new questions.

    Delivery App

    Web app to deliver order in secured, varifiable way across supply chain nodes.

    Built using Nodejs, Reactjs and Ethereum Blockchain.

    Web Scraper

    Tool built using Php and Php Simple HTML DOM Parser.

    It is used to extract data and different information from Stack Overflow website.

    Recipe Blog

    Who doesn't love food right!!.

    Page to view and add different recipes with user information built using Php with Mysql database.

    Article Blog

    Article Page made using Django with SQLite database.

    View and read different posted articles, login to the website and create your own pages and blogs.

    Typing Attack Game

    Typing attack is an educational game where user learns to type words quickly.

    Your mission is to type the words on balloons and destroy them before they reach the ground leading to game over.

    Snake game

    A fun game to play while waiting for things.

    Move the snake around with the arrow keys, eat the red dots to grow bigger, and avoid hitting your own tail.

    Ping-Pong

    Ping-Pong is built using Html5 canvas and Javascript.

    This game's goal is to hit the ping pong ball into opponent's goal makeing use of the keyboard arrow keys to control the paddles.

    Color-Walk

    Game built using HTML5 canvas with graphics drawn using Javascript.

    It is a game to select different color patches in the board presented in order to clear the board such as to get minimum score.

); }; export default Portfolio;
